<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='470510' id='t-470510'>At 400 meters, it missed me by three inches.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='472972' id='t-472972'>Just think about the math on that.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='477268' id='t-477268'>Every guy up there</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='479052' id='t-479052'>had some experience like that,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='480974' id='t-480974'>at least once, if not many times.</span>
</span>
</p>
<p class='talk-transcript__para'>
<data class='talk-transcript__para__time'>
 8:15
</data>
<span class='talk-transcript__para__text'>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='484502' id='t-484502'>The boys are up there for a year.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='486982' id='t-486982'>They got back.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='488751' id='t-488751'>Some of them got out of the Army</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='490110' id='t-490110'>and had tremendous psychological
problems when they got home.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='492704' id='t-492704'>Some of them stayed in the Army</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='494239' id='t-494239'>and were more or less okay, psychologically.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='497862' id='t-497862'>I was particularly close to a
