</span>
</p>
<p class='talk-transcript__para'>
<data class='talk-transcript__para__time'>
 9:36
</data>
<span class='talk-transcript__para__text'>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='565816' id='t-565816'>I think what he missed is brotherhood.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='570994' id='t-570994'>He missed, in some ways,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='572750' id='t-572750'>the opposite of killing.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='574146' id='t-574146'>What he missed was connection</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='576478' id='t-576478'>to the other men he was with.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='578826' id='t-578826'>Now, brotherhood is different from friendship.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='581342' id='t-581342'>Friendship happens in society, obviously.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='585096' id='t-585096'>The more you like someone,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='586634' id='t-586634'>the more you'd be willing to do for them.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='588708' id='t-588708'>Brotherhood has nothing to do</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='590214' id='t-590214'>with how you feel about the other person.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='593706' id='t-593706'>It's a mutual agreement in a group</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='596688' id='t-596688'>that you will put the welfare of the group,</span>
