</span>
</p>
<p class='talk-transcript__para'>
<data class='talk-transcript__para__time'>
10:22
</data>
<span class='talk-transcript__para__text'>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='611602' id='t-611602'>Brendan was a team leader</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='613000' id='t-613000'>in command of three men,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='614863' id='t-614863'>and the worst day in Afghanistan —</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='618300' id='t-618300'>He was almost killed so many times.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='621179' id='t-621179'>It didn't bother him.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='622514' id='t-622514'>The worst thing that happened to him in Afghanistan</span>
