<p class='talk-transcript__para'>
<data class='talk-transcript__para__time'>
11:21
</data>
<span class='talk-transcript__para__text'>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='670340' id='t-670340'>This wasn't invented recently.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='672772' id='t-672772'>Many of you have probably read &quot;The Iliad.&quot;</span>
